articles.description: Nico Carvacho had a career-high 26 points and a career-high-tying 20 rebounds to help Colorado State beat San Jose State 90-79 on Saturday.

videos.description: Trae Young hits his first 3-pointer from the Texas Longhorns logo.
videos.headline: Young knocks down first 3 of game

videos.description: Trae Young cuts inside and lofts a shot in over Mo Bamba for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young unleashes flotation device over Bamba

videos.description: Trae Young fires a 60 -foot pass to Rashard Odomes in transition for the dunk.
videos.headline: Young launches long ball to Odomes for dunk

videos.description: Trae Young tallies his 6th assist of the first half on a pass to Jamuni McNeace for the open dunk.
videos.headline: Young feeds McNeace for the slam

videos.description: Mo Bamba elevates for a missed shot and goes back up to draw the foul and get the bucket.
videos.headline: Bamba shows off reach on putback and-1

videos.description: Trae Young finds Rashard Odomes in transition after a Texas turnover to put the Sooners up 34-28.
videos.headline: Young leads fastbreak with 9th assist

videos.description: Kerwin Roach II anticipates the bounce pass from a trapped Trae Young and races in for the dunk, cutting the Longhorns' deficit to one.
videos.headline: Roach jumps Young's pass for dunk

videos.description: Oklahoma gets down the court in a hurry with four long passes leading to a Jamuni McNeace alley-oop without letting the ball touch the floor.
videos.headline: McNeace's oop completes full court OU break

videos.description: Trae Young leads with 9 assists at the half against the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Young's nine assists guide Oklahoma to first-half lead

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Young's nine assists guide Oklahoma to first-half lead) 2018/02/03 ESHEET

videos.description: Trae Young starts off the second half hot with a fast drive to the rim and a finger-roll finish.
videos.headline: Young drives in for finger roll

videos.description: Matt Coleman fools his defender and knocks down a 3-pointer to cut the Texas deficit to 50-46.
videos.headline: Coleman loses defender to hit 3

videos.description: Mo Bamba gets his 96th block of the season on Jamuni McNeace.
videos.headline: Bamba rejects McNeace on the hook shot

videos.description: Matt Coleman drives inside for a layup after a hectic sequence that is answered quickly by Trae Young with a long ball to Kameron McGusty.
videos.headline: Coleman scores off turnover, Young responds with full court assist

videos.description: Trae Young uses all his moves to get to the hoop but floats a pass to Jamuni McNeace for the alley-oop instead.
videos.headline: Young shows off handles on alley-oop to McNeace

videos.description: Kerwin Roach II cuts inside for the layup to put Texas up 70-66 after a 10-0 run for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Roach caps 10-0 run for Texas

videos.description: Trae Young tosses a perfect ball to Brady Manek for the alley-oop to make it 72-70 Texas.
videos.headline: Young lobs to Manek for the oop

videos.description: Eric Davis Jr. connects with Mo Bamba on the fast break as he finishes the alley-oop with style for the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Bamba reverse alley-oop dunk ices Oklahoma

videos.description: Trae Young scores 19 with 14 assists in Oklahoma's 79-74 loss to Texas.
videos.headline: Young gets double-double in losing effort
